{"word":"εὔκηλος 1","slug":"εὔκηλος 1","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n44239\" key=\"eu)/khlos1\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">εὔκηλος</orth> (A), <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ον</itype> (cf. Hdn.Gr.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg4085.tlg001:1:161\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.161</biblScope> </bibl>), <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Dor.\">Dor.</a></gram> </gramGrp> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">εὔκᾱλος</orth>, (v. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἕκηλος</foreign>) <sense id=\"n44239.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">free from care, at one's ease</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">εὔκηλος τὰ φράζεαι ἅσσ᾽ ἐθέλῃσθα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:554\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.554</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">εὗδον δ᾽ εὔκηλοι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:14:479\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">14.479</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg005.perseus-grc1:241\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ El.\">El.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">241</biblScope> </bibl> (lyr.); <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἡμεῖς μὲν . . πολέας τελέοντες ἀέθλους . . , ὁ δ᾽ εὔκηλος</foreign>. . <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:3:263\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.263</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">εὔκηλοι πολέμιζον</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:17:371\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">17.371</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">εὔκηλος τότε νῆα θοὴν . . ἑλκέμεν ἐς πόντον</foreign>, i.e. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">without fear</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0020.tlg002.perseus-grc1:671\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hes.\">Hes.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Op.\">Op.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">671</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0013.tlg004.perseus-grc1:480\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">h.Merc.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">480</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">εὔ. τέρπου φρένα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0486.tlg001:152\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Pherecr.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">152</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n44239.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> in Alexandr. and later <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ep.\">Ep.</a></gram> </gramGrp> of things, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">νὺξ εὔ.</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">still, silent</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0005.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:166\" default=\"NO\" TE